===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[milk]]-based [[product]] thickened by a [[bacterium]]-aided [[curdling]] process, and often mixed with [[fruit]] or other [[flavouring]]; any similar product based on other substances (e.g., soy yoghurt).

